  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate dextroamphetamine sulfate (sustained release) as an
      adjunct in cocaine treatment; an evaluation of the &quot;&quot;replacement&quot;&quot; strategy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
